barChartQuery.value: let usg_events = dynamic(["*"]);let grain = iff(true, 1h, 1h);  let mainTable = union pageViews,customEvents,requests     | where timestamp > ago(1d) | where isempty(operation_SyntheticSource) | extend name =replace("\n", "",name) | extend name =replace("\r", "",name) | where '*' in (usg_events) or name in (usg_events) ; let resultTable = mainTable; resultTable     | make-series Users = dcountif(user_Id, 'user_Id' != 'user_AuthenticatedId' or ('user_Id' =='user_AuthenticatedId' and isnotempty(user_Id))) default = 0 on timestamp from ago(1d) to now() step grain
